data.description: Natural light! End home with only one neighbor! Vaulted ceilings! Lots of parking! You'll enjoy these features plus a cozy fireplace, a spacious kitchen, and two decks to enjoy the beautiful views. The home has new hardwood floors in both the master and spare bedroom as well as a spacious primary bathroom. Near to the community pool & spa, Calavera Hills Community Park, and is located in one of the smaller, more private, buildings in the community. Easy access to the 5 and 78 freeways, and all that Carlsbad has to offer - shops, restaurants, the beach, and Carlsbad Village. Recent upgrades include a new water heater & new appliances!
